//000000604800a:3:{i:0;a:21:{s:10:"article_id";i:32;s:6:"cat_id";i:90;s:5:"title";s:12:"配送规范";s:7:"content";s:9718:"<p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">1、商品配送</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;"><br style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/></span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;"><br/></span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">1.1&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">卖家所选择的快递公司在派送商品时应当主动联系收货人，而不应在未征得收货人同意的情况下将商品交由小区保安、门卫、公司前台等人签收。</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;"><br/></span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">1.2&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">卖家应与快递公司约定，在提供配送过程中，应遵守一礼通平台相关规则规定的标准及规范，为消费者提供满意的配送服务，积极提升客户满意度。</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><br style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">2、商品签收</span></strong></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">2.1&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">卖家按照约定发货后，收货人有及时收货的义务。收货人可以本人签收商品或委托他人代为签收商品，被委托人的签收视为收货人本人签收。</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">2.2&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">消费者只填写了收货地址，但没有填写收货人或填写的收货人信息不特定，商品在收货地址被签收的，该签收视为消费者本人签收。</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><br style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">3、商品验收</span></strong></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">3.1&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">收货人签收商品时，应当对商品进行验收。</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">3.2&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">涉及商品表面一致的事项，收货人应当在签收商品时进行验收。本条所称“表面一致”，是指凭肉眼即可判断所收到的商品表面状况良好且与网上描述相符，</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">表面一致的判断范围包括但不限于商品的形状、大小、数量、重量等。</span><br/></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">3.3&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">收货人签收商品时发现表面不一致的，有权拒绝签收商品。卖家应在商品拒收后及时联系消费者，进行处理。</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">3.4&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">对于需要先签收再打开包装查看的商品，收货人应当要求承运人当场监督并打开包装查看，如发现表面不一致，应当在签收单（收货人联和承运人联）上备</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">注：详细情况并让承运人签字确认或者直接退回商品。</span><br/></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">3.5&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">收货人无正当理由拒绝签收商品的，运费由消费者承担。</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">3.6&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">收货人拒绝签收商品后，卖家应当及时联系承运人取回商品。因卖家怠于取回商品所产生的额外运费、保管费等费用由卖家承担。</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><br style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">4、风险转移</span></strong></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">商品毁损、灭失等的风险自收货人签收商品后由卖家转移给收货人。</span><br/></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><br style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;"/></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">5、违约处理</span></strong></p><p><span id="_baidu_bookmark_start_20" style="display: none; line-height: 0px;">‍</span></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">卖家违反本规范条款及一礼通平台相关规则约定而导致消费者投诉的，卖家应及时予以处理，若卖家未能妥善处理导致投诉扩大或未按照要求予以处理的，抠</span><br/></p><p microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" white-space:="" font-stretch:="" widows:="" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px;">一礼通有权以普通人身份做出判断并要求卖家承担相应的责任。</span><br/></p><p dir="ltr"><br/></p><p dir="ltr"><br/></p>";s:6:"author";s:0:"";s:12:"author_email";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:12:"article_type";i:2;s:7:"is_open";i:1;s:8:"add_time";i:1493720359;s:8:"file_url";s:0:"";s:9:"open_type";i:0;s:4:"link";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:5:"click";i:4571;s:12:"publish_time";i:1493740800;s:5:"thumb";s:0:"";s:9:"seo_title";s:22:"配送规范_一礼通";s:9:"goods_img";N;s:8:"goods_id";i:0;s:11:"is_ecommend";i:0;}i:1;a:21:{s:10:"article_id";i:33;s:6:"cat_id";i:90;s:5:"title";s:12:"配送声明";s:7:"content";s:3761:"<p microsoft="" font-size:="" color:="" text-indent:="" white-space:="" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 12px;">1、发货时间</span></strong><br style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/></span></p><p microsoft="" font-size:="" color:="" text-indent:="" white-space:="" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 14px;"><strong>1.1</strong>&nbsp;一礼通应当在一礼通规定的时间内发货，但有特殊规定的除外。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/><strong>1.2</strong> 消费者申请退款时一礼通尚未发货的，一礼通应当征得消费者同意后再发货。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/><strong>1.3&nbsp;</strong>一礼通延期发货，或者未经消费者同意在消费者申请退款后发货，一礼通应当追回已经发出的商品，但消费者已经签收并确认收货的除外。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p microsoft="" font-size:="" color:="" text-indent:="" white-space:="" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 12px;">2、发货信息的确认</span></strong><br style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/></span></p><p microsoft="" font-size:="" color:="" text-indent:="" white-space:="" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 14px;"><strong>2.1</strong> 除买卖双方另有约定外，一礼通应当按照订单约定的收货地址、收货人信息发货，并负责将商品送达到消费者指定的收货地址。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/><strong>2.2</strong> 如商品需要消费者到指定地点提取的，应当在商品页面显著位置描述予以说明，并在发货前告知消费者并征得消费者同意。一礼通违反前述规定的，消费者有权拒绝签收商品。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/><strong>2.3</strong>&nbsp;一礼通在发货后应及时将商品信息、快递信息在交易相关页面予以更新。</span><o:p></o:p></p><p microsoft="" font-size:="" color:="" text-indent:="" white-space:="" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 12px;">3、收货信息的填写与变更</span></strong><br style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/></span></p><p microsoft="" font-size:="" color:="" text-indent:="" white-space:="" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 14px;"><strong>3.1</strong> 消费者应当在订单中向一礼通提供准确的收货地址和收货人信息。消费者在提供收货人信息时，可以选择本人或者他人作为收货人。消费者选择他人作为收货人，该收货人违反本规范约定义务的，由消费者承担相应责任。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/><strong>3.2</strong> 消费者需要变更订单中的收货地址或收货人信息的，应当在商品发出前与一礼通取得联系征得一礼通的明确同意，或协商进行处理。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/><strong>3.3</strong> 因消费者填写的收货地址和(或)收货人信息不准确，或者未经一礼通同意要求变更收货地址或收货人信息，导致一礼通发货后商品无法送达的，运费由消费者承担。</span></p><p><br style="text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"/></p>";s:6:"author";s:0:"";s:12:"author_email";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:54:"配送声明，一礼通，发货规则，发货信息";s:12:"article_type";i:2;s:7:"is_open";i:1;s:8:"add_time";i:1493720428;s:8:"file_url";s:0:"";s:9:"open_type";i:0;s:4:"link";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:357:"一礼通应当在规定的时间内发货，但有特殊规定的除外，消费者申请退款时一礼通尚未发货的，一礼通应当征得消费者同意后再发货。关于延期发货，或者未经消费者同意在消费者申请退款后发货，一礼通应当追回已经发出的商品，但消费者已经签收并确认收货的除外。";s:5:"click";i:5365;s:12:"publish_time";i:1493740800;s:5:"thumb";s:0:"";s:9:"seo_title";s:40:"配送声明_一礼通发货配送规则";s:9:"goods_img";N;s:8:"goods_id";i:0;s:11:"is_ecommend";i:0;}i:2;a:21:{s:10:"article_id";i:34;s:6:"cat_id";i:90;s:5:"title";s:12:"配送范围";s:7:"content";s:4038:"<p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: verdana, " microsoft="" word-wrap:="" margin-top:="" margin-bottom:="" line-height:="" padding:="" border:="" list-style:="" color:="" white-space:=""><strong>市区范围配送市区范围配送市区范围配送</strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">1</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">、免运费</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">&nbsp;商家设定配送范围内的收货地址均不收取运费。客户购买此类商品无需支付运费。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">2</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">、满额免运费</span></strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">&nbsp;商家设定在商家店铺内购物满一定金额即可享受免收运费的优惠政策。当客户在一个商家店铺内购买此商家商品达到一定金额后，无须支付运费。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">、按地区收取</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">&nbsp;商家对发往不同地区，不同重量的包裹所需的运费进行设定。客户购买此类商品时，系统会根据商家设定自动计算所需运费。客户须连同商品及运费共同支</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">付。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">4</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">、发货时效</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">&nbsp;普通商品一般在客户下单后</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">1-2</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">天内发出，团购和促销商品一般在客户购买后</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">72</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">小时内发出。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">5</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">、快递方式</span></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-size: 9pt; word-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0pt;">&nbsp;购买商家商品时，由商家指定快递公司为您配送，如您有特殊需求，可以联系商家协商发货快递。</span></p><p><br/></p>";s:6:"author";s:0:"";s:12:"author_email";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:12:"article_type";i:2;s:7:"is_open";i:1;s:8:"add_time";i:1493720484;s:8:"file_url";s:0:"";s:9:"open_type";i:0;s:4:"link";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:5:"click";i:4334;s:12:"publish_time";i:1493740800;s:5:"thumb";s:0:"";s:9:"seo_title";s:22:"配送范围_一礼通";s:9:"goods_img";N;s:8:"goods_id";i:0;s:11:"is_ecommend";i:0;}}
?>